{"pin":"BH09970","subcodes":[{"code":"BH09970","anchor":"","first_line":"Say: O people, fear not the dominion of them that have oppressed and associated partners with God. Be ye steadfast in His Cause, then [3.5s]... ...When the victory arriveth, every man shall profess himself as believer and shall hasten to the shelter of God’s Faith","first_line_orig":"قل یا قوم لاتخافوا من سطوه الذینهم ظلموا و اشرکوا ان استقیموا علی الامر ثم ... قل اذا جآء النصر کل یدعون الایمان و یدخلون فی امر الله  ","language":"1","word_count":"90","subjects":"@steadfastness; perseverance; faithfulness, @call to action, @trust and reliance in God; turning to Him at all times, @consolation and comfort, @rejection, opposition and persecution, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#458\"\u003eLL#458\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Glea